  "title": "Credit Analyst (FINANCE MNC) - Central/up to $3.5k #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $3500<br />Duration: 1 year</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: <u><strong>Raffles Place</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p>Job Description:<br />•          Work with\ncorporate customers across Southeast Asia (Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand,\nPhilippines, Vietnam, etc.) to recover overdue commercial debts.</p><p>•          Negotiate\nrepayment plans and communicate professionally with buyers.</p><p>•          Handle customer\nenquiries and provide updates on case progress.</p><p>•          Record\ncollection activities using internal systems and tools.</p><p>•          Support your\nteam members with administrative tasks and learn the ins and outs of debt\nrecovery.</p><p><br /></p><p>Job Requirements: Min Diploma in Accountancy w min 2 yrs of relevant experience </p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p>",
